{"tid":1984626,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"徐英偉上任首日與工聯會屬下工會會面 商討利益輸送事宜","createTime":"2020-04-22T14:45:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T15:27:15.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"42797809feff8a65df6cfc7c4f295e7f8cdac22c","tid":1984626,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:45:48.000Z","msg":"徐英偉上任首日與工聯會屬下工會會面<br />\n22.04.2020 22:42<br />\n<br />\n新任民政事務局局長徐英偉，今日與立法會議員麥美娟，以及工聯會屬下的護衛及物業管理從業員總會，和香港環保物流及清潔從業員協會代表會面，就防疫抗疫基金下的物管支援計劃安排交流。工會要求計劃範圍擴展至私人住宅以外的樓宇，徐英偉承諾會將資助範圍延伸至工商廈，並擴大相關資助名額，表示會盡量以簡單、快捷及寬鬆的原則處理申請。<br />\n<br />\n民政事務總署表示，物管支援計劃截至今日已收到超過8100宗申請，當中超過1800宗申請已獲批核，涉及超過1.4萬幢樓宇，佔全港私樓總數超過四成，資助金額超過6300萬元。而就資助範圍擴大至工商廈的詳情，署方短期內會公布細節。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282683&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1282683%26csid%3D261_341&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6Cvpmn865KX7g3oX29oYbiiE%3D&h=c5a78763\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282683&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"00a25a9e0ed4f88ed078cae3afda2728b5636f44","tid":1984626,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T15:14:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/825076/org/836b3dac45becd9b189de88ee7075c4a.jpg/pooLymK5jtPtQCGsdeS3wIs0pqvVAZoZ1kQmm9ZEJps?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F825076%2Forg%2F836b3dac45becd9b189de88ee7075c4a.jpg%2FpooLymK5jtPtQCGsdeS3wIs0pqvVAZoZ1kQmm9ZEJps%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=740e236c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d55443d76fed490a02254a447f2cc8f793253725","tid":1984626,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T15:27:15.000Z","msg":"賊眉賊眼<br />\n最適合做condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}